node.text:
Joe Biden just said there are no indications that Americans have struggled getting to the airport in Kabul. 

This is not true! But the President’s media friends didn’t press him on it.

“A source tells me, “Situation [in Afghanistan] is rapidly deteriorating… We’ve had Americans get beaten throughout the night.” One of them, an American woman, was beaten “twice” even though she was carrying a U.S. passport.” 

“Yesterday @PentagonPresSec said Americans are not being impeded as they travel to the Kabul airport, no Americans harmed. The Taliban agreed to let them evacuate. What I am hearing suggests otherwise. Americans have been injured and stopped from boarding planes.” 

“I’m also told Taliban is targeting Afghans US worked with, “going door to door and executing anyone that has worked with the US.” That “Taliban are searching the cars at checkpoints to find out something related to the foreign countries specially United States.” Separate sources.”
~ source Sasha Ingberg / twitter

node.title: Joe Bide has no idea what is going on. They’re all saying different things

node.text:
FOR UNILATERAL DECISION-MAKING AND BOTCHED AFGHAN WITHDRAWAL 

President Trump never drew the level of criticism on display yesterday from the U.K. Parliament,  who angrily aligned from across the political aisles to hold Joe Biden in contempt for his unilateral withdrawal from Afghanistan without discussing the issues with NATO.

According to British media,  Joe Biden would not take the calls from U.K. Prime Minister Boris Johnson for 36 hours as the crisis unfolded.  The British and allied forces were scrambling to secure their own troops and diplomats with no guidance or contact from the White House.

Labour and Conservative parties expressed a united anger and frustration toward a failed and inept U.S. administration.

Notice at the end he does not mention the United States. They have zero trust in America at this point. Sad 😢

node.title: BRITISH PARLIAMENT HOLD JOE BIDEN IN CONTEMPT

node.text:
If you haven’t heard this radio transmission, please take the time to listen. ⛔️Be cautioned it is hard to listen to.⛔️

The calm voice in the chaos  in Chicago during the incident that occurred on 8/7/2021. Thank you Dispatcher Keith Thornton - The way he took control of this incident and talked to his officers, kept his air completely shut down and clear, set a perimeter within seconds quite possibly is what resulted in the apprehension of the suspects. 

Dispatcher Keith Thornton was fast thinking and took initiative without any direction in the very beginning stages and ran the emergency like an actual incident commander - far beyond the criteria of any dispatcher. 

The world heard you loud and clear and we stand with you. 💙🖤💙🖤💙🖤💙
#chicago #dispatcherlife #policedispatcher #bluelivesmatter #chicagopolicedepartment #keiththorton #policeofficer #police #lawenforcement

After COVID-Stricken Migrants Seen ‘Coughing, Sneezing’ at a Restaurant. 

HIDALGO COUNTY, Texas (CBSDFW.COM) – The La Joya Police Department issued a public health announcement after an officer approached an undocumented migrant family at Whataburger who told him Border Patrol released them because they had COVID-19.

On July 26 the police department of the small town along the Rio Grande and Mexican border shared details of the incident. They said a concerned citizen at the restaurant waved down the officer. The citizen told him about the family “coughing and sneezing without covering their mouths and not wearing face masks.” Whataburger management also told the officer that they wanted the group to leave as well due to “their disregard to other people’s health.”

They say "We should all be vaccinated!" They want to lock us back down and issue covid passports

If things couldn’t get worse in Afghanistan. At Kabul airport today. Rumors that the Americans will take anyone that gets through so tens of thousands have arrived.

Biden has managed to cause the exact same border crisis at both the U.S. southern border and at the perimeter of the international airport in Afghanistan, by saying virtually the same thing. 

Remember the chaos he caused in Mexico, Guatemala and Honduras when he said; “I would in fact make sure that there is, that we immediately surge to the border — all those people are seeking asylum. They deserve to be heard,” Biden said. “That’s who we are. We’re a nation that says, ‘If you want to flee and you’re fleeing oppression, you should come.’”
Flee they did. And come they did, surging. Some came wearing Biden T-shirts reading, “Biden, please let us in.” We’re still seeing hundreds arriving daily. Our Border is still In chaos 

Biden in his ABC News interview on Wednesday: 

"There are Afghan women outside the gate. I told 'em, 'Get 'em on the planes. Get them out. Get them out. Get their families out if you can.’" ~ White House Correspondent Charlie Spiering said on twitter

node.text:
Joe Biden just said there are no indications that Americans have struggled getting to the airport in Kabul. 

This is not true! But the President’s media friends didn’t press him on it.

“A source tells me, “Situation [in Afghanistan] is rapidly deteriorating… We’ve had Americans get beaten throughout the night.” One of them, an American woman, was beaten “twice” even though she was carrying a U.S. passport.” 

“Yesterday @PentagonPresSec said Americans are not being impeded as they travel to the Kabul airport, no Americans harmed. The Taliban agreed to let them evacuate. What I am hearing suggests otherwise. Americans have been injured and stopped from boarding planes.” 

“I’m also told Taliban is targeting Afghans US worked with, “going door to door and executing anyone that has worked with the US.” That “Taliban are searching the cars at checkpoints to find out something related to the foreign countries specially United States.” Separate sources.”
~ source Sasha Ingberg / twitter

"Yesterday, the White House said that Joe Biden has not taken any calls with world leaders in regards to Afghanistan," GOP strategist Amy Tarkanian tweeted. "Justin Trudeau stated that he spoke with Hillary Clinton yesterday about Afghanistan. What is going on? Why is the US President not taking calls but Hillary is?" Why is Kamala Harris speaking with Canada instead of Hillary? 

WE DO NOT HAVE A LEADER IN THE WHITE HOUSE!! 

"I guess if there’s one person who really knows about failed foreign policy leaving Americans stranded in hostile territory it’s her," said Republican communicator Matt Whitlock.

Nancy praise Joe Biden, and Hillary Clinton is allegedly now fielding calls with world leaders while U.S. Allies, World Leaders Blast Biden Over Afghanistan Debacle, Question U.S. Resolve

Yesterday, the White House said that Joe Biden had not taken any calls with world leaders in regards to Afghanistan.

Justin Trudeau stated that he spoke with Hillary Clinton yesterday about Afghanistan.

What is going on? Why is the US President not taking calls but Hillary is?

Where is QueMala Harris? Why isn’t she the one calling World leaders and why is Hillary?

node.text:
FOR UNILATERAL DECISION-MAKING AND BOTCHED AFGHAN WITHDRAWAL 

President Trump never drew the level of criticism on display yesterday from the U.K. Parliament,  who angrily aligned from across the political aisles to hold Joe Biden in contempt for his unilateral withdrawal from Afghanistan without discussing the issues with NATO.

According to British media,  Joe Biden would not take the calls from U.K. Prime Minister Boris Johnson for 36 hours as the crisis unfolded.  The British and allied forces were scrambling to secure their own troops and diplomats with no guidance or contact from the White House.

Labour and Conservative parties expressed a united anger and frustration toward a failed and inept U.S. administration.

Notice at the end he does not mention the United States. They have zero trust in America at this point. Sad 😢

node.text:
The US Embassy in Afghanistan under the direction of Joe Biden just sent out a second security alert to stranded Americans in Kabul:
“THE UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT CANNOT ENSURE SAFE PASSAGE TO THE HAMID KARZAI INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT.”

You are on your own.

But not the UK. They put their citizens FIRST above all else. The British Government reportedly sent Special Forces Para Troops in vehicles through the center of Kabul to rescue their citizens.

According to British media,  Joe Biden would not take the calls from U.K. Prime Minister Boris Johnson for 36 hours as the crisis unfolded.  The British and allied forces were scrambling to secure their own troops and diplomats with no guidance or contact from the White House.

The UK sent paratroopers to Kabul to help rescue the 4,000 stranded British Citizens and Afghan helpers in the city.  They were told to “prepare for face-to-face combat.”👍🏽

British Parliament has since came out and forcefully slammed Joe Biden in Contempt For Unilateral Decisionmaking and Botched Afghan Withdrawal. America has shown weakness under Joe Biden.

Joe Biden’s Administration says we, the United States, do not have the capability to do this, meanwhile British and French Special Forces are able to go in and save their citizens. 

Why is Joe Biden such a coward?

This is incompetence of the highest order, what a complete disaster. This is starting to look like Joe Biden’s Benghazi.
